## Testing Strategy

### Unit Tests
- Vitest, Vue Test Utils, Vue Testing Library
- Coverage: authentication, payment logic, key UI components.

### Integration & E2E Tests
- Deferred until after initial functionality stabilizes.

### CI/CD
- Minimal setup using GitHub Actions.
- Ensure unit tests pass before merging.
